        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "REUSABLE MULTIPURPOSE TOOL: From cable management and food storage to school supplies and pantry organization, ToolTreaux’s 24 pack of kitchen grade silicone zip ties or twist ties can do it all and will prove handy to have around the house, home office, workplace or garage for a multitude of tasks; And, they’re reusable!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "CORD & CABLE MANAGEMENT: Our bag of assorted silicone twist ties will work on virtually any cable! Whether it be an HDMI cable, basic power cords or an extension cord, these zip ties are made to keep your cables safe and organized, helping you achieve a clutter-free office or workspace",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "SEAL FOOD BAGS: Another use for our multipurpose silicone ties is to properly seal a variety of bags in your home; Our cable ties ensure you get the most out of your bread, keep pantry items fresh and will even keep your garbage bags sealed, ensuring a neat and tidy, organized kitchen, fridge, freezer, pantry and much more",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "FOOD PREP: A unique aspect of these silicone twist ties is that the twist ties are food grade approved, meaning you can use our multifunctional zip ties to blanch vegetables or seal food; utilizing these zip straps can help keep food items fresh",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "HANG ACCESSORIES: These zip ties are notably strong and very durable; because of this, the twist ties can be used to hang a wide variety of items such as lanterns, or attach water bottles to a hiking backpack; a perfect tool to accompany you on family camping trips or trekking adventures",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                }
            ],
            "is_required": true,
            "source": "catalog",
            "asin": "B0933RJK56",
            "raw_value": true
        },
